Class GUIAbstractModule

java.lang.Object
  abstractModulePack.GUIAbstractModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
GUIInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
GUIModule
public abstract class GUIAbstractModule
extends java.lang.Object
implements GUIInterface

This module implements some basic functionalities of a GUI module. A GUI with more functionalities can be implemented by extending this class.
